						<div class="postbody">They didn't fix it in Sonic 2:
<br />
<br /><img src="http://img245.imageshack.us/img245/3592/sonic06.png" alt="Image" /> -&gt; <img src="http://img80.imageshack.us/img80/9445/sonic07.png" alt="Image" />
